<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Wanderlog — Travel Stories</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Libre+Baskerville:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Nunito:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --earth: #2d1f0e;
    --sand: #c4a77d;
    --sky: #6b8fa8;
    --leaf: #4a6741;
    --cream: #faf7f2;
    --warm-gray: #8a7a6a;
  }
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { background: var(--cream); color: var(--earth); font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    background: rgba(250,247,242,0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(196,167,125,0.3);
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 0 3rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    height: 65px;
  }
  .nav-logo { font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .nav-logo span { color: var(--sand); }
  nav ul { list-style: none; display: flex; gap: 2rem; }
  nav ul li a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    transition: color 0.3s;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  nav ul li a:hover { color: var(--earth); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--leaf);
    color: white !important;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.8rem !important;
    font-weight: 600 !important;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--earth); color: white !important; }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    height: 85vh;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1a3040 0%, #2d4a2d 35%, #4a3520 70%, #2d1f0e 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .hero-terrain {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 40%;
    background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(45,31,14,0.9) 0%, transparent 100%);
  }
  .hero-stars {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: radial-gradient(1px 1px at 20% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.8) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 70% 15%, rgba(255,255,255,0.6) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 40% 60%, rgba(255,255,255,0.4) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 85% 45%, rgba(255,255,255,0.7) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 15% 75%, rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 0%, transparent 100%);
  }
  .moon {
    position: absolute;
    top: 12%;
    right: 18%;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 35%, #ffedc2, #f0c060 50%, #c4903a);
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(212,168,67,0.4), 0 0 80px rgba(212,168,67,0.15);
  }
  .mountain {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20%;
    font-size: 12rem;
    opacity: 0.15;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 3rem 3rem 4rem;
    color: white;
  }
  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(107,143,168,0.3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(107,143,168,0.5);
    padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #a8cce0;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--sand); }
  .hero p { max-width: 50ch; font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-hero-primary {
    background: var(--sand);
    color: var(--earth);
    border: none;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .btn-hero-primary:hover { background: white; }
  .btn-hero-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: white;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .btn-hero-secondary:hover { border-color: white; }

  /* STORIES SECTION */
  #stories { padding: 5rem 3rem; }
  .section-intro { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .section-intro h2 {
    font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  .section-intro p { color: var(--warm-gray); font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .section-intro .divider {
    width: 50px; height: 3px;
    background: var(--sand);
    margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .stories-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: auto auto;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .story-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(45,31,14,0.06);
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .story-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(45,31,14,0.12); }
  .story-card.featured { grid-row: span 2; }
  .story-img {
    height: 240px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 6rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .story-card.featured .story-img { height: 320px; }
  .story-small .story-img { height: 160px; font-size: 4rem; }
  .story-region {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1rem; left: 1rem;
    background: rgba(45,31,14,0.7);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .story-body { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .story-meta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--warm-gray); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .story-title {
    font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--earth);
  }
  .story-card.featured .story-title { font-size: 1.6rem; }
  .story-excerpt { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--warm-gray); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .story-read-more {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--leaf);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    transition: gap 0.3s;
  }
  .story-read-more:hover { gap: 0.7rem; }

  /* ABOUT SECTION */
  #about {
    background: var(--earth);
    color: white;
    padding: 5rem 3rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  #about h2 { font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  #about h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--sand); }
  #about p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); line-height: 1.9; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .about-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
  .stat-num { font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--sand); }
  .stat-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); letter-spacing: 0.1em; }

  /* NEWSLETTER */
  #newsletter {
    background: var(--leaf);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }
  #newsletter h2 { font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  #newsletter p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .newsletter-form { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; max-width: 420px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .newsletter-form input {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.2rem;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    color: white;
  }
  .newsletter-form input::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
  .newsletter-form button {
    background: var(--sand);
    color: var(--earth);
    border: none;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .newsletter-form button:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

  footer {
    background: var(--earth);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">🧭 <span>Wander</span>log</div>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#stories">📖 Stories</a></li>
    <li><a href="#about">🌍 About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#newsletter">✉️ Newsletter</a></li>
    <li><a href="#newsletter" class="nav-cta">Follow Along</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg">
    <div class="hero-stars"></div>
    <div class="moon"></div>
    <div class="mountain">🏔</div>
    <div class="hero-terrain"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-tag">✦ Stories from the road</div>
    <h1>Life is short.<br><em>Travel far.</em></h1>
    <p>Three trips, three continents, infinite moments. Join me as I chase sunsets, stumble through language barriers, and fall in love with every corner of this beautiful world.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#stories" class="btn-hero-primary">Read the Stories</a>
      <a href="#about" class="btn-hero-secondary">About the Author</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="stories">
  <div class="section-intro">
    <h2>Recent Adventures</h2>
    <p>Three stories from three different worlds</p>
    <div class="divider"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="stories-grid">
    <!-- Featured story -->
    <div class="story-card featured">
      <div class="story-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3040, #2d4a6a);">
        <div class="story-region">🇳🇵 Nepal</div>
        🏔️
      </div>
      <div class="story-body">
        <div class="story-meta">
          <span>📅 January 2025</span>
          <span>⏱ 12 min read</span>
          <span>🏷 Trekking</span>
        </div>
        <div class="story-title">Above the Clouds: 21 Days on the Annapurna Circuit</div>
        <div class="story-excerpt">I didn't know what altitude sickness felt like until my body decided to throw a full tantrum at 4,200 metres. But somewhere between the burning lungs and the prayer flags flapping in the Himalayan wind, I found something I didn't know I was looking for...</div>
        <a href="#" class="story-read-more">Read Story →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Small stories -->
    <div class="story-card story-small">
      <div class="story-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3a2010, #6a3a20);">
        <div class="story-region">🇲🇦 Morocco</div>
        🌅
      </div>
      <div class="story-body">
        <div class="story-meta"><span>📅 October 2024</span><span>⏱ 8 min</span></div>
        <div class="story-title">Lost in the Medina: A Fes Love Story</div>
        <div class="story-excerpt">Getting lost was the plan all along.</div>
        <a href="#" class="story-read-more">Read →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="story-card story-small">
      <div class="story-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #204030, #406030);">
        <div class="story-region">🇨🇷 Costa Rica</div>
        🌿
      </div>
      <div class="story-body">
        <div class="story-meta"><span>📅 August 2024</span><span>⏱ 6 min</span></div>
        <div class="story-title">Pura Vida: The Philosophy of Slow Travel</div>
        <div class="story-excerpt">Two weeks. No agenda. Just a hammock and the sound of howler monkeys.</div>
        <a href="#" class="story-read-more">Read →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="about">
  <div>
    <h2>Meet the <em>Wanderer</em></h2>
    <p>I'm Maya, a freelance writer and chronic traveller with a weakness for strong coffee and questionable Wi-Fi. I've been documenting my journeys since 2019 — not to show off, but because writing is how I process the world.</p>
    <p>This blog is my travel journal, made public. The messy parts included.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="about-stats">
    <div><div class="stat-num">34</div><div class="stat-label">Countries Visited</div></div>
    <div><div class="stat-num">6</div><div class="stat-label">Years Travelling</div></div>
    <div><div class="stat-num">120+</div><div class="stat-label">Stories Written</div></div>
    <div><div class="stat-num">3</div><div class="stat-label">Bags Lost</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="newsletter">
  <h2>✉️ Never Miss a Story</h2>
  <p>New adventures, honest travel tips, and the occasional rant. No spam, ever.</p>
  <div class="newsletter-form">
    <input type="email" placeholder="your@email.com">
    <button onclick="alert('Subscribed! 🌍')">Subscribe</button>
  </div>
</section>

<footer><p>©️ 2025 Wanderlog by Maya · Made from airports, hostels, and rooftops around the world</p></footer>

</body>
</html>
